        public int compareTo(Book other)
        Compares this book to the specified book. The result is the equal to the difference this book price value - other book price value.
        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable<Book>
        Parameters:
        other - a book to compare
        Returns:
        a positive value if the price value of this book is greater than the price value of the other book, a negative value if the price value of this book is less than the price value of the other book, or zero if both books have equal price values.
